{
  "texts": [
    "CC markets and blockchain technology have been studied extensively.",
    "For instance, Xu et al. (2019) provide detailed reviews of current academic research on blockchain and CC trading.",
    "Sebastião and Godinho (2021) examined the predictability of three major CCs (Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Litecoin) and analyzed the profitability of trading strategies devised by machine learning techniques.",
    "Regarding the CC market efficiency, several studies have been conducted on the particular price behaviors of these assets.",
    "However, previous studies have provided mixed results regarding this issue despite most of the literature supporting the inefficiency of CC markets."
  ]
}